  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Fluocinolone Acetonide Intravitreal Implant</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Masked, Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of an Intravitreal Fluocinolone Acetonide Implant in Subjects With Non-Infectious Uveitis Affecting the Posterior Segment of the Eye</official_title>
  <sponsors>
